* {{IPA|/ˈraɪdə(r)/}}
* {{SAMPA|/"raId@(r)/}}
* Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-aɪdə(r)|-aɪdə(r)]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# one who [[ride]]s, often a horse or motorcycle
# {{politics}} a [[provision]] [[annex]]ed to a [[bill]] under the consideration of a [[legislature]], having little connection with the subject matter of the bill
# an [[amendment]] or addition to an entertainer's [[performance]] contract, often covering a performer's [[equipment]] or food, drinks, and general comfort requirements

